name: 743 names
description:
743 names is an action game about a spy named Jeff Jones. Jeff goes through 9 separate missions, trying to investigate the terrorist organization KRAB and ultimately prevent the operation known as "Operation: Flaming Catacombs".

Features:

  • 9 levels
  • Action-packed gameplay
  • Interesting story
  • Pixel art
  • James Bond theme (royalty free)
  • 1-2 hours of gameplay

Controls:

Arrow keys to move, jump, and walljump. You cannot change velocity in midair.

Tap X to fire bullets.

Hold Z to use stealth. In stealth, henchmen cannot see you, but you move slower, and you cannot shoot. Refill your stealth timer by spending time outside of stealth.
